Pearson's Dynamic Study Modules leverage deep brain research to help students acquire more information faster, remember it longer and recall it accurately when it counts - on quizzes, tests and final exams.

For more information, please click here.

Trouble logging in?

Please find here some tips that can help you.

1. Verify you have a subscription to a valid Pearson title that contains Dynamic Study Modules.

2. Launch Dynamic Study Modules from your MyLab / Mastering Course Home from your computer.

3. Remember that your login information is the same as your Mastering or MyLab login, which you can retrieve from this link.

4. Still can't login? Please contact our 24/7 Technical Support for assistance: via email, chat or phone.
